{
  "texts": [
    "RQ5: Who are the most cited authors on green financing and renewable energy?",
    "This paper explores the connection between circular economy and supply chain concepts through a bibliometric analysis of articles published up to 2024 in Web of Science (WoS) and Scopus.",
    "The analysis focuses on the top 10 journals by the number of articles with the keywords \"circular economy\" and \"supply chain\" and the citation count.",
    "The study also compares WoS and Scopus indexing to assess their impact on the literature.",
    "A keyword map was created using VOSviewer (version 1.6.17) to explore the topic further."
  ]
}